item.description:
@I_Yaa_I wrote:

[quote=“darklord1, post:19, topic:305102”]hi this is how i did it.

1)search for login.java

2)do ctrl+f and typ in chris

3)click enter once and wen it finds what you typed in do ctfl+h on the top line keep the name chris up and on the bottom put your username there

4)once one that click replace all now save and go into cmd folder and compile

5)once done that search for commands.java

6)and do the same in commands.java as what you did in login.java

Hope this helped.[/quote]
